ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: I say so if I am angry or sad.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I like to talk with a few chosen people when things get too much for me.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I make an active effort to find a solution to my problems.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: Physical exercise is important to me.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I think something positive could come out of my complaints/problems.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I firmly believe that my problems will decrease (and my situation improve).
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I try to forget my problems.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I put my problems behind me by concentrating on something else.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I bury myself in work to keep my problems at a distance.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I often find it difficult to do something new.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I am well on the way towards feeling I have given up.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely

ElementDescription: I withdraw from other people when things get difficult.
Notes: 0= Disagree Completely; 1= Tend to Disagree; 2= Yes and No; 3= Tend to Agree; 4= Agree Completely
